  "StockRole": "Command Mech",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Radius came out of the Jihad in tiny numbers and nearly all of them were destroyed before the war ended, so finding one operational is genuinely unusual. The Word of Blake built it as a network anchor, and in that role it makes every allied unit around it more dangerous without firing a single shot. A mech that wins fights by making its teammates better is a rare thing to find at this weight class. Blake hardware always makes me uneasy, but I cannot argue with what it does.",
